snippet.title: XING: The Land Beyond - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
A new atmospheric puzzle-adventure game set in the Afterlife, coming out on September 18th, 2017 for PC, Oculus Rift and HTC Vive!

Find out more at: http://www.xingthegame.com/
